marki. Taka wsp\u00f3\u0142praca mo\u017ce by\u0107 bardziej efektywna kosztowo w por\u00f3wnaniu do Instagrama.<\/li>\n<li><b>Monitoruj kampanie PPC<\/b>: Regularnie analizuj swoje kampanie reklamy PPC na Amazonie. Zwr\u00f3\u0107 uwag\u0119 na ACoS (Advertising Cost of Sales) i dostosuj stawki, aby zoptymalizowa\u0107 wydatki na reklam\u0119.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, kluczem do sukcesu w sprzeda\u017cy na Amazonie jest zrozumienie swojego produktu oraz odpowiednie dostosowanie strategii reklamowych. Zastosowanie powy\u017cszych wskaz\u00f3wek pomo\u017ce Ci zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 widoczno\u015b\u0107 i przyci\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 nowych klient\u00f3w.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak wykorzysta\u0107 reklamy na Amazonie i TikToku w bran\u017cy Beauty i FMCG?<\/h1>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6810,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6809","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6809"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6809"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6809\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/6810"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6809"